  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/244359.htm", 
  "description": "<p><strong>感谢<a href=\"http://www.ming4.com/192.168.1.1/\" target=\"_blank\">192</a>的投递</strong><br /></p><p>美国专利和商标局通过了一项苹果申请的“惯性和触摸感应混合输入设备”，这份专利将传统输入设备，比如鼠标、轨迹球和触控板的优点融合在一起，打造成单一的产品。我们都知道，电脑的鼠标使用光学传感器，轨迹球和滚轮控制屏幕上的鼠标箭头。苹果MacBook产品线上配备的多点触控触摸板使用小区域内的电容信号追踪运动，其他类型的设备使用加速器和惯性传感器侦测运动。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e87bacd/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244359.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E6%96%B0%E4%B8%93%E5%88%A9%EF%BC%9A%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8%E3%80%81%E8%A7%A6%E6%8E%A7%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8B%E4%B8%80%E4%BB%A3%E6%B7%B7%E5%90%88%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244359.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E6%96%B0%E4%B8%93%E5%88%A9%EF%BC%9A%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8%E3%80%81%E8%A7%A6%E6%8E%A7%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8B%E4%B8%80%E4%BB%A3%E6%B7%B7%E5%90%88%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244359.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E6%96%B0%E4%B8%93%E5%88%A9%EF%BC%9A%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8%E3%80%81%E8%A7%A6%E6%8E%A7%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8B%E4%B8%80%E4%BB%A3%E6%B7%B7%E5%90%88%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244359.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E6%96%B0%E4%B8%93%E5%88%A9%EF%BC%9A%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8%E3%80%81%E8%A7%A6%E